  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Advanced NSCLC

          -  18 years or older

          -  A life expectancy of at least 12 weeks

          -  Presence of a malignant lesion within the chest of at least 0.5 cm diameter as
             measured by computed tomography (CT)

          -  Written informed consent

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Claustrophobia

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Metal implants in the thorax
      </textblock>
